{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Financial Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #a52a2a; /* Brownish red */\n            --secondary-color: #d2b48c; /* Tan, a less contrasting color */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --hover-color: #8b0000; /* Darker red for hover effects */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #d2b48c 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0 0 10px 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n\n        #main-nav {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        #main-nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n\n        #main-nav li {\n            display: inline;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        #main-nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #main-nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/a52a2a/ffffff?text=Financial+Growth+Abstract') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(165, 42, 42, 0.6); /* Red overlay */\n        }\n\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            font-style: italic;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h3, #about h3, #contact h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .about-text {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .about-text:hover {\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(165, 42, 42, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Ensures padding doesn't affect width */\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .fade-in {\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; }\n            to { opacity: 1; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Financial Consulting</h1>\n            <p>Strategic Solutions for Your Financial Future</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav id=\"main-nav\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#hero\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\" class=\"fade-in\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Unlock Your Financial Potential</h2>\n            <p>Expert guidance for sustainable growth.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container fade-in\">\n        <h3>Our Services</h3>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h4>Investment Strategy</h4>\n            <p>We craft personalized investment plans aligned with your risk tolerance and financial goals.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h4>Wealth Management</h4>\n            <p>Comprehensive strategies to grow, preserve, and transfer your wealth effectively.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h4>Risk Assessment</h4>\n            <p>Identifying and mitigating financial risks to ensure stability and security.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container fade-in\">\n        <h3>About Apex</h3>\n        <div class=\"about-text\">\n            <p>Apex Financial Consulting is dedicated to providing sophisticated financial advice with an artistic approach to planning. We believe in fostering long-term relationships built on trust, transparency, and a deep understanding of our clients' aspirations. Our team of seasoned professionals is committed to navigating the complexities of the financial world for your benefit.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container fade-in\">\n        <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n        <form id=\"contact-form\">\n            <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n            <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n            <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n            <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n            <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Financial Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n            const sections = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in');\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = '1';\n                    }\n                });\n            }, { threshold: 0.1 });\n\n            sections.forEach(section => {\n                observer.observe(section);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}